<subSubSection id="C301F0D2FFA7FF88A3A9FE1EFE006531" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA4A359FFA7FF88A3A9FE1EFE006531" blockId="20.[151,1437,330,609]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A3A9FE1EFE9C66FD" bold="true" box="[151,256,403,429]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Remark.</emphasis>
It was reported from 
<collectingCountry id="F30CE3C9FFA7FF88A2C5FE1EFDFC66FD" box="[507,608,403,429]" name="Morocco" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Morocco</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A1B5FE1EFCA666FE" author="Alluaud, C." box="[651,826,403,430]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="12 - 28" refId="ref24728" refString="Alluaud, C. (1926) Compte rendu d'une mission zoologique dans le Maroc Sud oriental (Avril Mai, 1924). Bulletin de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles du Maroc, 6 (1 - 6), 12 - 28." type="journal article" year="1926">Alluaud (1926)</bibRefCitation>
, Orchymont (1935) and 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A76AFE1EFB6766FD" author="Kocher, L." box="[1108,1275,403,429]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="77 - 117" refId="ref27094" refString="Kocher, L. (1938) Localisations nouvelles ou interessantes de Coleopteres Marocains. Bulletin de la Societe de Science Naturelle du Maroc, 18, 77 - 117." type="journal article" year="1938">Kocher (1938)</bibRefCitation>
, but we could not study the material. Since then, no new records have been published; however, two very close species, 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BD8DAFFA7FF88A3F8FE56FE5566A5" authorityName="Ienistea" authorityYear="1988" box="[198,457,475,501]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Ochthebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridescens">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A3F8FE56FE5566A5" box="[198,457,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Ochthebius viridescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BD8DAFFA7FF88A2C3FE56FD0B66A5" authorityName="Ganglbauer" authorityYear="1901" box="[509,663,475,501]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Ochthebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fallaciosus">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A2C3FE56FD8D66A5" box="[509,529,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">O</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A120FE56FD0B66A5" box="[542,663,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">fallaciosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were recently collected in 
<collectingCountry id="F30CE3C9FFA7FF88A081FE56FBB466A5" box="[959,1064,475,501]" name="Morocco" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Morocco</collectingCountry>
. Furthermore, 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BD8DAFFA7FF88A7F4FE56FAAF66A5" authorityName="Peyron" authorityYear="1858" box="[1226,1331,475,501]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Ochthebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridis">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A7F4FE56FAAF66A5" box="[1226,1331,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">O. viridis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a relict Eurosiberian species (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A280FE72FD276549" author="Valladares, L. F. &amp; Diaz, J. A. &amp; Garrido, J. &amp; Sainz-Cantero, C. E. &amp; Delgado, J. A." box="[446,699,511,537]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" refId="ref28842" refString="Valladares, L. F., Diaz, J. A., Garrido, J., Sainz-Cantero, C. E. &amp; Delgado, J. A. (2018) Coleoptera Hydraenidae. In: R. Sanchez, M. A. (Ed.), Fauna Iberica. Vol. 44. Museo Nacional de Ciencias Naturales, Madrid, pp. 1 - 516." type="book" year="2018">
Valladares 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A103FE72FDEA6549" box="[573,630,511,537]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
); and this species had already been excluded by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A7DBFE72FE88656D" author="Jach, M. A. &amp; Delgado, J. A." pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="199 - 231" refId="ref26830" refString="Jach, M. A. &amp; Delgado, J. A. (2008) Revision of the Palearctic species of the genus Ochthebius Leach. XXV. The superspecies O. (s. str.) viridis Peyron and its allies (Coleoptera: Hydraenidae). Koleopterologische Rudschau, 78, 199 - 231." type="journal article" year="2008">Jäch &amp; Delgado (2008)</bibRefCitation>
. Thus, we consider that the identification of this species should correspond to one of the two above mentioned species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
